Discovery Engine API.

## Quickstart

The main types to work with this crate are the clients:

- [CompletionService]
- [ControlService]
- [ConversationalSearchService]
- [DataStoreService]
- [DocumentService]
- [EngineService]
- [GroundedGenerationService]
- [ProjectService]
- [RankService]
- [RecommendationService]
- [SchemaService]
- [SearchService]
- [SearchTuningService]
- [ServingConfigService]
- [SiteSearchEngineService]
- [UserEventService]
